{"tid":2355490,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"想既包裹去英國 請問邊間物流公司好","createTime":"2021-01-06T06:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T21:44:57.000Z","uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0015fec71c1e7ddd8672c46df315ef5fb1aebf","tid":2355490,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"本身想用香港郵政因為最便同最方便<br />\n但啱啱問咗而家淨係得返平郵<br />\n小弟唔想女朋友咁耐先收到<br />\n<br />\n啱啱上網用咗計算運費呢個工具<br />\n但依家小弟冇箱 唔知所有嘢加埋一齊個箱係幾闊幾長同幾高<br />\n亦都唔知所有野加埋一齊係幾重<br />\n所以都做唔到計算運費<br />\n所以依家唔知點做好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢到就係大概想寄既野 <br />\n有無巴絲俾到意見 用咩物流公司比較好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3ab253a875b4dae16f2eabfc566d4a7772346a","tid":2355490,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:50:24.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"ff079e977a77c488aea512669d18fe9635cbb023","tid":2355490,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:50:37.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"fedf72931360cb25a356f0bc47c4e5928b46cdb2","tid":2355490,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ed49b3d95e8c7f8a0a9f25c41b7c946702a05941","tid":2355490,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"c8e4ba6bc3624f3bdde9312fc4b7a7f969be9363","tid":2355490,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:52:40.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"0cafc34c286957206d205939372883ae0b4836b8","tid":2355490,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"4c8dd5a73ac2762acbd4180cba7dc0376ab2fdd1","tid":2355490,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:53:52.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"47db9f57d56f41d5eebe948cc